@node Main "ezaMaze - Documentation"

                             'ezaMaze' V2.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'ezaMaze' is a maze @{"game" link play} where the goal is to find the exit in the
least amount of moves possible. To complicate matters a little, in
each game the exit is located at a different position and not
necessarily on the edge of the labyrinth, in fact the exit might be
located right in the middle of the labyrinth!

  As if it was not enough, only a small portion (a 7 by 7 tile area)
of the labyrinth is shown. To help you, an arrow indicates where the
exit is located from your current position.

  You can choose the size of the labyrinth you want to play with!

  Have fun!

